<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="frightening-adj">frightening <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fraɪtnɪŋ/    美 /'fraɪtnɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>令人害怕的；吓人的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a frightening experience / thought
可怕的经历/念头</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Going into hospital can be very frightening for a child.
对孩子来说上医院可能很可怕。</p></div></div>